label: Of the parabola
attribution: Provided by the University of Pennsylvania Libraries.

metadata.label: Description
value: Consists of the definition and construction of the parabola with 58 propositions in geometry, each illustrated with a diagram.

metadata.label: Extent
value: 39 leaves : paper, illustrations ; 198 x 163 (168 x 123) mm bound to 204 x 170 mm

metadata.label: Note
value: Table of contents: Last section of the volume comprising propositions 43 through 58 is titled "The use of the parabola in projectiles" (p. 53-74).
Pagination: 39 leaves; [ii, 1], 2-72, [73-76]; contemporary pagination in ink, upper outer corners.
Script: Written in a cursive script by a single hand.

metadata.label: Physical Location
value: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts, Manuscripts, Ms. Codex 526
